      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, this is a good start. Could you make it sound a little less \"templated\"? Maybe add a sentence or two that feels a bit more personal/warm, so they don't feel like just another number in the system, but keep it strictly professional. We really liked their personality during the interview.",
