      "content": "Subject: Your Application for the Senior Dev Role\n\nDear [Candidate's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I wanted to take a moment to thank you for your interest in the Senior Dev role at our Austin-based company. Your enthusiasm and dedication to your craft were truly evident throughout the interview process, and we appreciate the time and effort you invested in sharing your skills and experiences with us.\n\nAfter careful consideration and thorough evaluation, we have decided to move forward with another candidate who possesses a more extensive background in AWS architectures. This decision was not made lightly, as we were impressed by your technical prowess and the unique perspectives you brought to the table.\n\nWhile we believe you have the potential to excel in many roles, we feel that your current skill set aligns more closely with positions at a different seniority level. We encourage you to continue honing your skills and expanding your expertise, as we are confident that you will find a role that perfectly matches your talents and aspirations.\n\nWe genuinely enjoyed getting to know you and your passion for technology. Your personality shone through during our conversations, and we were genuinely impressed by your enthusiasm and drive. We hope you will keep us in mind for any future opportunities that may arise, and we wish you all the best",
